edu.harvard.integer.service.discovery

Class IpServiceElementSeed

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.integer.service.discovery.IpServiceElementSeed
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class IpServiceElementSeed
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class holds the information needed to do a service element discovery. This is passed to the discovery process to define what to discover and how to discover the devices.
